241
00:19:53,480 --> 00:19:54,340
apa?

242
00:19:54,340 --> 00:19:55,180
Pernahkah anda mendengar

243
00:19:55,710 --> 00:19:56,870
bahagian belakang
Gunung Void?

244
00:19:58,630 --> 00:19:59,630
